{"per_page":10,"total":14,"current":11,"data":[{"title":"Orcale存储过程事物","date":"2018-07-11T22:37:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/145","categories":["DataBase"]},{"title":"Orcale存储过程demo和走的坑","date":"2018-07-10T22:37:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>orcale的坑<br><strong>1、定义的存储过程的名一定要和最后END的时候的名字一样</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">create or replace procedure &quot;Pro_Sprk_Cancel&quot;(</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br><span class=\"line\">as</span><br><span class=\"line\">...</span><br><span class=\"line\">begin</span><br><span class=\"line\">end &quot;Pro_Sprk_Cancel&quot;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p><strong>2、存储过程中用的一切参数一定要定义</strong><br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">create or replace procedure &quot;Pro_Sprk_Cancel&quot;(</span><br><span class=\"line\">)</span><br><span class=\"line\">as</span><br><span class=\"line\"> --定义变量</span><br><span class=\"line\"> num number;</span><br><span class=\"line\">drug_num number;</span><br><span class=\"line\">begin</span><br><span class=\"line\">  begin</span><br><span class=\"line\">     select count(1) into drug_num from &quot;his_system_drug_info&quot; ;     </span><br><span class=\"line\">     select count(1) into num from &quot;his_pharmacy_storage&quot; ;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     end;    </span><br><span class=\"line\">end &quot;Pro_Sprk_Cancel&quot;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/137","categories":["DataBase"]},{"title":"plsql 永久注册码适用各个版本","date":"2018-07-09T22:11:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/136","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"php 小数整理,向上取整,向下去整,四舍五入,丢弃小数部分,保留整数部分","date":"2018-07-05T23:23:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/135","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"微信小程序获得服务器ip","date":"2018-07-03T02:53:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>错误：<br>    有时候在小程序前端能取到图片的地址，但是不显示<br>解决方法：<br>    可能是数据库中只存了图片的服务器地址，但是地址不全<br>    例：<br>    <figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">/pages/member/info/index</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>\n<p>但如果要显示到页面上需要加ip。即：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">192.168.100.103/pages/member/info/index</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/134","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"数据库在新建表的时候添加注释comment on column","date":"2018-07-02T20:02:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/133","categories":["DataBase"]},{"title":"微信小程序—如何获取用户输入文本框的值k.detail.value","date":"2018-07-02T03:51:00.000Z","excerpt":"<p>1、前端<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&lt;view&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;view&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&lt;textarea class=&quot;text &quot; bindinput=&quot;change&quot;  placeholder=&quot;请输入你想说的话......字数200字以内 &quot;&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;/view&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&lt;button bindtap=&quot;submit&quot; class=&quot;btn btn-success block &quot;&gt;提交评价&lt;/button&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&lt;/view&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/131","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"问题在哪就去哪找！切记！切记！","date":"2018-06-28T23:21:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/129","categories":["Life"]},{"title":"微信小程序的缓存问题小知识","date":"2018-06-26T03:32:00.000Z","excerpt":"<h3 id=\"1，缓存小demo\">1，缓存小demo<a href=\"post/128#1，缓存小demo\"></a></h3><p>方法顺序也是执行顺序<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">onShow: function () &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   this.getcity();</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;，</span><br><span class=\"line\">//把城市数据放到缓存中</span><br><span class=\"line\"> getcity: function () &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   var t = this;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   wx.getStorage(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">     key: &apos;city&apos;,</span><br><span class=\"line\">     success: function (res) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">       console.log(res.data);</span><br><span class=\"line\">       if (res.data) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">         t.setData(&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">           city: res.data</span><br><span class=\"line\">         &#125;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">         t.calcDistance();</span><br><span class=\"line\">       &#125; else &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">         t.calcDistance();</span><br><span class=\"line\">       &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">     &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   &#125;);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"> &#125;,</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>","link":"post/128","categories":["Other"]},{"title":"git提示服务器与本地有冲突","date":"2018-06-26T03:24:00.000Z","excerpt":"","link":"post/126","categories":["Git"]}]}